is Wieck]] |- |2017 || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Eddie Williams (strongman)|Eddie Williams]] || {{flagicon|AUS}} Vernon Van Schalkwyk || {{flagicon|AUS}} Jean-Stephen Coraboeuf |}
