'''Ruensley Anthony Leuteria''' (born 17 June 1992) is a [[Association football|football]] player from [[Curaçao]], currently playing for the [[Curaçao national football team|national football team of Curaçao]]. He debuted internationally in a friendly against [[Aruba national football team|Aruba]] in a 2–0 victory. In September 2018, he scored his goal against [[Grenada national football team|Grenada]] in a 10–0 victory.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.concacafnationsleague.com/en/nations-league-qualifying/game-detail/440454#tab_match=match-details|title=Game Detail|website=www.concacafnationsleague.com}}</ref>
